Fortuna is commonly represented in art with a ship's helm in her right hand, and in her left the horn of Amaltheia,


<A ID="p243x"></A>which was placed among the stars; hence here <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">mundanam</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
