"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">141</A>
The reference is to the fourteen regions into which Rome was divided by Augustus. Nicomedia, in the opinion of good judges of such matters, was worthy to be considered a fifteenth region of Rome.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note142" HREF="
