E/Roman/Texts/Ammian/22*.html#ref179
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">179</A>
His two motives were: a love of action; and, since those men had prayed to him for peace who no one ever thought would do so, a desire for further glory in the Orient.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
