Not the one at Delphi, but a spring at Daphne, a suburb of Antioch.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note188" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Ammian/22*.html#ref188
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
