"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">202</A>
The <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">victimarius</SPAN> slew the animal that was offered up.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
