E/Roman/Texts/Ammian/22*.html#ref204
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">204</A>
One of the divisions of the night; the latter part of the fourth watch; <I>cf.</I> <A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Pliny_the_Elder/5*.html#80
	"TARGET="Pliny"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Pliny,WIDTH,205)"
