<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note205" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Ammian/22*.html#ref205
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">205</A>
Socrates; perhaps referring to the saying quoted by Stobaeus, <I>Sermones</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">CCXIII</SPAN><!--</A>STOBAEUS--> <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">πόσῳ μᾶλλον χαριέστερον ἐποίησας, εἰ καὶ τούτους</SPAN> (= <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">ἐχθρούς</SPAN>) <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">εἰς φιλίαν μετετρόπωσας</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note206" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Ammian/22*.html#ref206
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">206</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
